<taxonomicName id="4C714D2281C7FF6BFDFBFB4AFC30FAC6" box="[631,899,1274,1300]" class="Liliopsida" family="Orchidaceae" genus="Saccolabium" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asparagales" pageId="232" pageNumber="233" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="flexuosum">
<emphasis id="B905EAB381C7FF6BFDFBFB4AFC30FAC6" box="[631,899,1274,1300]" italics="true" pageId="232" pageNumber="233">Saccolabium flexuosum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
has been attributed to 
<bibRefCitation id="EFE04B5081C7FF6BFB05FB4AFAD1FAC7" author="Lindley, J." box="[1161,1378,1274,1301]" pageId="232" pageNumber="233" pagination="1 - 63" refId="ref224800" refString="Lindley, J. (1858) Contributions to the orchidology of India II. Journal of the Proceedings of the Linnean Society of London 3: 1 - 63. https: // doi. org / 10.1111 / j. 1095 - 8339.1858. tb 02055. x" type="journal article" year="1858">Lindley (1858: 36)</bibRefCitation>
, but it was actually made by 
<bibRefCitation id="EFE04B5081C7FF6BFE0DFAAEFD2CFAEB" author="Reichenbach, H. G." box="[385,671,1310,1337]" pageId="232" pageNumber="233" pagination="886" refId="ref227003" refString="Reichenbach, H. G. (1864) Saccolabium flexuosum. Annales Botanices Systematicae (Walpers) 6: 886." type="journal article" year="1864">Reichenbach (1864: 886)</bibRefCitation>
.
